{"tid":1802353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民陣1.1大遊行已獲批NONO, 到時維園見!!!","createTime":"2019-12-29T11:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T11:32:44.000Z","uid":310684,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ca074e1ee0fda937b00bd1a110de84bf5a1802df","tid":1802353,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:49:29.000Z","msg":"資料轉自民陣 fb<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【元旦大遊行　不反已出】<br />\n<br />\n民陣已收到警方發出的不反對通知書，<br />\n可以正式同各位講多次，1.1 維園見！<br />\n<br />\n元旦遊行當日將會有超過 40 個新成立工會同大家見面，歡迎大家了解詳情，加入你所屬行業的工會，壯大抗爭的組織力量。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘承諾，並肩同行，五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n一月一，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【民陣元旦大遊行】<br />\n2020.1.1 星期三 Wednesday｜2PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to <br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;"},{"pid":"dc02551491f16f8e426c40e5f9950bef77b9d7bf","tid":1802353,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gYeZ0g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gYeZ0g.png&h=aeae6f0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"096ee8bd1d738b09c52bba24084d38ac2eb1b7b2","tid":1802353,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:54:14.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"ed6dae45dcaccf4c94813585fa48019fbd5927b6","tid":1802353,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:54:26.000Z","msg":"月"},{"pid":"5962bc9bf88ede86d6687fc134c84fe90108f68b","tid":1802353,"uid":310684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T11:54:36.000Z","msg"